**SPELLS** (20) <br>
2 <!--355-->Shockwave <br>
3 Fireball <br>
2 <!--393-->Thermal Blast <br>
3 <!--392-->Syphon Vortex <br>
2 <!--498-->Thunderquake <br>
3 <!--548-->Firefly Swarm <br>
2 <!--550-->Wildfire <br>
3 <!--680-->Lava Flow   </FONT></TD></TR><TR><TD WIDTH="10%" VALIGN="TOP"><font face="Haettenschweiler, Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif" size="5" COLOR="#000000">Strategy</Font></TD><TD><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2">1st Magi: Raega <br>
Raega is a great starting Magi for this type of deck. You&#39;ll usually want to go second, so that you can start Cremating right away. Starting with Braggle makes her an excellent Magi and the Arbolit is only gotten if there is a Corrupt in play. <br>
<br>
2nd Magi: Valkan <br>
Valkan is a Spell playing master. Provided that you were able to successfully stall long enough to get spells with Raega, here&#39;s what you want to do with Valkan: <br>
Play Robe of the Ages and Scroll of Fire. Play Giant Arboll. Play tons of Spells. Energy Transfer from Giant Arboll back to Valkan. Play even more Spells. <br>
<br>
3rd Magi: Amanax <br>
Amanax is backup, in case Valkan is defeated. He also plays Spells and can gain from them. Like in my other deck, starting with Syphon Vortex is a plus. <br>
<br>
**CREATURES** <br>
Arbolit - Tech vs. The Dark Twins. Starting for Raega. <br>
Ergar - Direct damage deck:Direct damage Creature. <br>
Braggle - Starting for Raega. Great stalling card too. <br>
Giant Arboll - Every time you play a Spell, this guy gets energy! Play with Valkan, play as many Spells as possible, give energy back to Valkan, play more Spells! <br>
<br>
**RELICS** <br>
Scroll of Fire - I wonder why this is in here... <br>
Relic Stalker - Hmmm... Doesn&#39;t really take a Rocket Scientist to figure out that if you lose Pyromancy, you lose the game. Take that Belt away... <br>
Robe of the Ages - I&#39;ll pay one energy to deal five damage to any Creature. Great fun! <br>
Abraxin&#39;s Crown - Spells just don&#39;t cover enough ground. Fortunately, you have this! <br>
Rayje&#39;s Sword - Tech vs. Burrow decks and Zannah. <br>
<br>
**SPELLS** <br>
Shockwave - Take out that Pylofuf. <br>
Fireball - Direct damage Spell. Need I say more? <br>
Thermal Blast - See Fireball <br>
Syphon Vortex - Great with Amanax (no kidding). <br>
Thunderquake - Amazing with Valkan vs. weenie swarm decks. <br>
Firefly Swarm - See Fireball <br>
Wildfire - See Thunderquake <br>
Lava Flow - See Fireball  </FONT></TD></TR><TR><TD WIDTH="10%" VALIGN="TOP"><font face="Haettenschweiler, Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif" size="5" COLOR="#000000"> </Font></TD><TD><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2">DeckTech <BR> For the Players, By the Players  <BR>www.decktech.net </FONT></TD></TR></table> 
